      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older example in poor overall condition and best suited for a project, restoration candidate, or parts/repair use. It shows heavy cosmetic wear, age-related deterioration, and a tired interior, and buyers should expect multiple needs rather than a turn-key driver. This is not a show car and not something I\u2019d oversell\u2014plan on deferred maintenance, repairs, and recommissioning work before regular use. If you want an honest car to take on as a budget project, this is that kind of vehicle.",
