    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition car that shows normal age and wear inside and out, but should still be a usable driver for someone not expecting a perfect example. Expect visible cosmetic imperfections, some tired spots, and the kind of maintenance items and aging you\u2019d typically see on an older vehicle, but it remains a decent candidate for basic transportation, a budget buy, or a light improvement project. It\u2019s not mint and not a junker either\u2014just a straightforward older car being represented as it is.",
