      "description": "Affordable transportation with solid everyday utility, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a buyer who values value over cosmetics. It shows its age and wear, but remains a straightforward, budget-friendly option with dependable basic function and plenty of life left for the right owner. A smart pick for commuting, a first car, or a backup vehicle at an accessible price.",
