    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs affordable wheels, a backup car, or a project to tinker with. Plenty of life and usefulness left for the right buyer, and priced to reflect its condition while still offering good value. If you\u2019re after cheap transportation without the big price tag, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-focused project with solid bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, steering feels direct, and the chassis still has the kind of planted, analog character enthusiasts look for. Cosmetically it shows age and it will need attention, but that also makes it an honest platform for someone who wants a usable budget car, weekend tinkering project, or straightforward restoration candidate. A great opportunity to get into a capable machine at an accessible price.",
      "price": 7900.0,
