      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real grit and personality\u2014the kind of ride that still shows up with purpose and invites its next owner to make it their own. It has the seasoned, honest presence of a vehicle that\u2019s lived a full life, with plenty of story left for commutes, weekend errands, or as a hands-on project for someone who appreciates potential over polish. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive wheels with character and a can-do attitude, this one delivers that rare mix of affordability and opportunity.",
